data.description: Just a short distance from the Columbia River, on nearly half an acre, this 1515 square foot updated home, with 3 bedrooms & 2 full baths has everything you need! As you, walkthrough the home, you will notice beautiful hemlock wood trim on door frames and window frames. This home built in 1975 is anything but original, with full updates, the home feels modern with character. The backyard is also equipped with a private Double RV parking space, with full hookups including a power station and dumping station, this is a rare feature! Newer Water Heater and Newer HVAC that have been regularly maintained service this home. Beautifully updated and immaculately maintained, this home is ready for its next owners! Call today to schedule a showing!
